snippet.title: Redout Announcement Trailer Rework
snippet.description:
** CHECK THE NEW TRAILER AND PREORDER NOW! **
http://store.steampowered.com/app/517710/
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mr_BQyO6MbI


--// For further informations, please visit 34bigthings.com or follow us on Facebook! \\--
34BigThings proudly presents, the Redout launch trailer revamped! Here you can see the progress we made in the last 4 months and the current state of the project.
Redout is still planned to land on PC and consoles in 2016.
